sub_title: Translator of English & Dutch at Double Check Translations
summary:
Experienced sworn translator of English-Dutch / Dutch-English, conveying the message clearly and accurately, recreating the source text to suit any target audience. 

Fields of expertise: Legal translation, Sworn translations, Music & Education. Legal documents, certificates &  diplomas, websites, insurance, tourism, culinary translation and more.
